\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't - just now and again. Sometimes on a weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would you all join in singing?
