\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember your mother or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423226\charrsid9257172 father}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
