\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So occasionally you had family prayers at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Yes.
