mostly I think we played. And playing ball as well. Bat and ball and skipping. Sometimes - with a bat and ball or another time - do a lot of skipping in them days, all children did. And used to have - used to have swings as well. On the school railings an
d all that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were you allowed to get dirty when you played?
