\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they emphasise certain things as important in life?
