\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  British and Foreign school they called it. British - British and Foreign. It was a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 peculiar}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  name wasn't it? School on it's own - a very nice school.
