\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh quite a lot, there was like two or three - three classrooms I think.
