\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, don't - they were never there then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you feel about cleaning the school that you went to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh we knew - we knew it was helping mother so we didn't worry you see. Used to help - helped one another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 Did the other children come from similar types of home to your own?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, very similar, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did the teachers single out some children for different treatment from the others or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 There - there might have been odd ones, only very odd ones if there were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember what type of person was a pet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Don't know anything about - there was none really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were there any gangs or groups in the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't think so, I don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were there any children left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, never noticed - never noticed any.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You didn't go to another school afterwards did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 NA.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You left school at fourteen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, we went to work straight away.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would you have stayed longer if you'd had the opportunity?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I might have done, they let them stay 'til they were fifteen then.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you attend any part time education afterwards, did you go to any evening classes or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No, I didn't go to any other, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. None whatever.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you think you benefited from attending school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, it was a nice school and schoolmasters at both very nice. Oh yes, everybody liked them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Why was that, were they old men or young men?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well - well the headmaster was middle aged and the other one was not very ol
d - just in between like. Always meant - always gentlemen teachers I - we had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you prefer gentlemen teachers to ladies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well - well there's no other there, that's all there was in that school, there was no lady teachers, except the very litt
le ones, the primary. The very little ones and that's only that they had.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 While you were at school did you have a part time job or any means of earning a little regular money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Only - only running errands sometimes for people. Sometimes an errand, that's al, just occasionally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Your first full time job, you went to Hartlepool did you as soon as you left school? Or did you go somewhere else? When you left school what did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 When I first left school I went - I went to - I went to 
Hartlepool to help someone who was ill and I stayed about a month. Just temporary you see that. Yes. Some friends of the schoolmaster where I had been living in Thirsk. Some relations of theirs it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You were only there a month?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just a month while she had her second baby. Looking - looking after the little girl as well and taking her out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you get that job? Did you live in there?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I got that through the schoolmaster. Yes, I lived in with them, yes. They were relations of the s
choolmaster's and they asked would I go just for a month.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And you just sort of helped?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Helped - looked after the little girl and helped do a few jobs in the house. I was only fourteen then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were there any other servants in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No, just ordinary. Not much, it's only a month you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You got it through the schoolmaster?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, they were relations -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You did jobs in the house and looked after the little girl?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just the odd jobs like washing up and things like that. I took the little girl out mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What hours would you say you worked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you know what time you got up?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I was up by about eight o'clock I think.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have to work at the weekends, did you have a half day or any holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, just all work - just worked right through.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What were you paid?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Forgotten now. Can't think what they give me now. In them days didn't pay much at all did they. About five shillings a week, it wouldn't be any more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you feel that was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I never - never used to worry 'cos it was only temporary you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you give any of the money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Give it all to her. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What would she spend it on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh on food - anything as we wanted - that she wanted I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you get on with the family that you worked for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh very well. Yes, they were very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she employ anyone else there at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No, just - just her and her husband an her - his mother lived with - her mother lived with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did she treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh very well. Just like herself - just like the family.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you like the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes, never worried about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You took a living in job after that with your auntie and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, at - that was at Hartlepool in a fruit - fruit - fruit and - and - fruit and a mixed business. Fruit and - and groceries as well.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You lived in there did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Lived in - I was with them - eight and a half years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And it was your auntie?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Aunt and uncle, yes. On mother's side that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So you were there until just before the first world war with that aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I didn't get a wage in them days. They give me pocket money if I went home - if I wen
t home for the weekend. And used to buy all me clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you come to go to them, what made you decide to go and help in the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well they just took it over and they asked me to go. And I was with them right until they - they left the shop the first war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You were with another auntie and uncle before that, during the war they changed over didn't they?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, well this is the first one. I was there eight and a half years with them, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What exactly did you have to do, what was your job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well I used to have to do - I used to have to do housework. Yes. And help in the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 shop}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  when I got finished. And then I went out - went out with orders as well. Used to often take orders out. Yes, did work hard in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What hours would you say you worked then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Well it was opening time eight o'clock and we didn't close while - what time did we close, oh all - they used to be open seven - while seven some nights. There was no restrictions straight away, but there was after a 
few years. After a few years we had to close at six. And then eight on a Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So when you weren't doing housework you were in the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have to work Saturdays and Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Didn't open on a Sunday no, Saturdays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have a half day at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, had a half day on a Monday I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, this - this is Wednesday half day. It would be Wednesday wouldn't it. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have any holidays with pay while you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, didn't have - I just - when I had any I was generally just }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 home}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  for the weekend. Didn't have holidays in the days, I just went home for a weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They didn't pay you anything, they gave you pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Pocket money - just a few shillings, that was all. They bought my clothes you see. And food you see, I got me food and clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And they just gave you a few shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 That's about all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they pay your fare home or anything when you went home?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes, they paid me fare when I went home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they give you more money then when you went?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They used to give me perhaps five shillings.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you feel this was fair treatment or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well you didn't think anything wrong in them days did you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you give any of the money to your mother, you couldn't very well could you because it was only your pocket money?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, 'cos there wasn't much over.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What did you spend your pocket money on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Don't know really. I di
dn't spend it, I just save it for - sometimes I had some I saved a bit up, then I went home I did give mother it if I had any over. I used to buy sweets sometimes, not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you get on with the other people you worked with, who lived there, who was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423226\charrsid9257172 Aunt}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  and uncle that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No other children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No other help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well - they had a - they had - my - this aunt had married a - a widow you see and his family was all grown up - and married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So there were just the three of you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just that three of us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And they didn't employ anyone else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you get on all right with your aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes, got on well, had a lovely time.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were you fond of your aunt?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, very.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you feel about the work, did you like it or dislike it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Both very kind to me, yes. Well I just helped - I worked in with them you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 There were no other servants were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you live as a part of the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, just lived in with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was your aunt interested in what you did, were you allowed out any time to do just what you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I - I only went down - went to church sometime - went on a - if I ever I wanted to go to the church or do t
here. I didn't go - we didn't go -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she bother about what time you came home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I never - never - never was out late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Where did you sleep when you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 In a little bedroom at the back.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 A room of your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have your meals with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, we all lived together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you feel homesick at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No, never, was always happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you make any friends round about there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes. Next door people, next door girl, same age as me. 
A girl, yes. She'd knock on the wall to me sometimes, used to knock on the wall when she went to bed at night. Like that, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was there anything you particularly liked or disliked about that situation, about living with your aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't - don't think - I was happy all the time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did the housework go, did you do the cleaning?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 She used to get someone in the - for the - the special cleaning, we did the other ourselves between us like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Occasionally you had someone to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 When she wanted to paper and that, but she did a lot of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 papering}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  herself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you do the ordinary day to day cleaning up, or did your aunt do it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, I did - I used to do it in the morning before I went in the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was the washing sent out or done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Used to light the fire when I first got up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You were kept busy weren't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I was only - fourteen years old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was the washing sent out or was it done at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Some was done at home and some was 
sent out, with having shop she hadn't time. She sent all the wash - all the boiling things out. She only washed coloured things at home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you help with that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometimes, when I got older I did, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who made or mended the family's clothes, there was only herself and her husband?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well my - my aunt used to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who did the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 She did the cooking. I used to help with it sometimes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who was responsible for repairs and improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 My uncle I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Where did you have your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 In the - in the -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How many rooms were there in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 In the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How many rooms were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 There was a living room and a - there was a living room and a kitchenette and a 
- and then there was - front room upstairs you see, being a shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So there was a living room and a kitchenette downstairs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Then the sitting room was upstairs and the two bedrooms. Three bedrooms rather, there was three bedrooms.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you all have breakfast together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, always have together, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What did she cook on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Bacon - sometimes bacon, sometimes - just - just ordinary breakfast. Bread, butter and marmalade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And just the three of you had it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Together, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she have a range or a gas cooker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 She'd a gas cooker.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So you all had breakfast together and sometimes it was bacon, what else did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Bread butter and marmalade.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have anything different on Sundays when you'd got a bit more time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well - sometimes we'd have eggs as well. Bacon.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have your main meal in the middle of the day or at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Generally after we closed generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So what did you have in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just - just had a light meal in the middle of the day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What would you normally have for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just some - I should think meat pies or - or meat and - or meat and - potatoes you know, something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And then you had your cooked meal at night did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What did you have for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Always some kind of meat. I don't know what really, sometimes we had rabbit, sometimes chicken. All different things. 'Cos we used to sell chicken in them days. Specially at Christmastime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You'd be all right with having the shop wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, wouldn't be short of food. Never short of food.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 On Sundays when the shop was shut did you have your main meal in the middle of the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 We had it at twelve o'clock. After service.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What sort of a tea would you have on Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh just a - fruit - sometimes fruit. And cakes and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 All three of you were always having your meals together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 All }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 together}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
. Yes, we always had them together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Any supper at all during the week or on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 We generally a cup of tea and - and perhaps a biscuit or something.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was that the same on Sunday as well?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Unless we was - very hungry. We had what we wanted, it was just left to us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were any of the following made in the house, bread, jam, bottled fruit and vegetables, pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, she used to bottle - make jam, she used to bottle fruit.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she make her bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, she didn't make bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 But she made jam and she bottled fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 She did - she did all her cooking - her own baking like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she ever bottle vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 But - I don't think she bothered with bread, we used to buy bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she ever do any pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometimes yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You don't think she did vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't think she bothered with vegetables, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they ever make any wine or beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't think so. Ginger wine she used to make at Christmas. Homemade ginger wine. Yes, homemade ginger wine, I remember that. At Chri
stmastime, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Any medicines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, she didn't make - anything of that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 This was your auntie was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were fruit and vegetables grown, did they have a garden as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They had a garden for a while then they had 
to give it up, it was too much for uncle, he had too far to go to it, it was a mile away. Used to grow - potatoes and vegetables but it got too much for him so he had to give it up. He had it for a few years, then he gave it up. Just bought them off the m
en then.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were any bought for the household, you'd have them in the shop wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, all in - we used to - I don't know if she kept account what we spent, I expect she would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they ever have any tinned or dried vegetables or fruit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 Maybe tinned ones, there's always been tinned ones as long as I can remember hasn't there?. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't know about dried ones then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they keep any livestock for the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423226\charrsid9257172 family,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  any hens, pigs or goats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Only a cat sometimes, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How many times a week would you eat meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh every - every - every day sometime.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was any tinned meat used?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, not much I don't think, no, used to cook it mostly. I was there when the first world war started, 1914 I was there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Can you remember anything the family did together on Christmas Day, did you go to church on Christmas Day or not when you were at }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 Hartlepool}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 We generally went once, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was this chapel or church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 The Wesleyan chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember anything else you did on Christmas Day together with your aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I can't remember. Only looking at the cards and things like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you usually go home for Christmas or did you stay with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Not often - I used to come more in summer than Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were there any musical instruments in the home at Hartlepool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, they had a little organ.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who played that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Uncle played that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt or uncle sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometimes on Sunday nights sometimes have a - only us three there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was that hymns?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, always plenty of books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Any newspapers or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 He had newspapers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember your aunt or uncle reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Used to read the Bible every night, I remember that. Every night and every morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they read it out aloud?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. We always had family prayer. That's very old fashio
ned isn't it? Now. Only time - all the time I was at Merry Street, all the time I was with them we had family prayer every morning. Before he opened the shop.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Your uncle did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 before}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
 he opened the shop, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just the three of you had family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just aunt together, he - he give the - he always gave the prayer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did he do any reading then from the Bible?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 He did at night, used to read a chapter.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 He must have been a very religious man?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes he was. He was local preacher as well. In these days they don't do that now do they. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were you impressed by it, did you enjoy it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh I - I just took it - all in - in - in the stride with everything else you see. 'Cos I knew they were - I knew they were - ver
y - very religious, I knew that when I went to them like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember a funeral in that family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 We'd never - we'd never any wrong word, we were always happy together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They were good living people were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Always yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember a funeral in that family? Your aunt and uncle were alive at the end of the first world war weren't they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Oh yes, they were there after the first world war and then a year after they moved to - to - another village. They gave the shop a
nd - and another aunt and uncle took it and I stayed with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you go out with your aunt and uncle at all? Did you ever go out together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometimes we walked out - not very far, not very often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever go anywhere else with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't remember, no, don't remember much about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever go with your aunt and uncle when they went away on a holiday or to stay with people?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, they didn't go away in them days. I used to go to Thirsk sometimes on a market d
ay with her. 'Cos she used to go and buy eggs and butter at the market, at Thirsk, and I used to sometimes go with her. Sometimes - if she was poorly I used to go, if she couldn't go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Is that where they had to go to the market from Hartlepool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, right to Thirsk. But she didn't do it for - only for so long, she had to give it up in the end.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes, wouldn't let you work on a Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they go to chapel every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Mostly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And you went to chapel as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you go to Sunday school then or were you too old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, not - didn't go to Sunday school then, only at Thirsk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you all sit together when you were at chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was grace said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes it was in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And you did have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle take an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Not very much I don't think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember if they ever passed an opinion about the Government or anything like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't remember much about politics really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your uncle take part in sport, go to races or play cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. I know he was - I know he was a Liberal, that's all I know. Yes. That's all I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was your aunt the same?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your uncle take part in sport or go racing?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, no. No he never did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Or play cards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 He was always in the garden working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did he go to a club at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. They didn't in them days much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your auntie ever go out on her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she have any interests outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she do any work for charities or sit on any committees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Don't think - no, I don't remember, she was too busy with the shop you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle go out together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Where would they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well sometimes they'd go to }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 Hartlepool}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  to the promenade for a break like. You know, all - Hartlepool, that - that's - that's West Hartlepool where the shop was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 But they'd go to where you called Old Hartlepool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Round where the sea was, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was your uncle ever away from home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No. Never had any holiday all the time I was there. Just only weekend - only weekends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle have friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes they had plenty of friends in the church. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they ever stay in the house or did they just come to visit?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, no, just come to - see 'em temporary then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What kind of people were these friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just - oh they were nice people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would you say they were the same class as your aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, was all the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were they shopkeepers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well some of 'em were shopkeepers and some weren't. Some of 'em working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What class would you say they were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I should say - ordinary people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was your aunt more or less the same class as your uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, yes, just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle treat any of their friends differently from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, they - no, they made everybody }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 welcome}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever come across the customers in the shop? What sort of people were the customers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh they were all very nice people. But in them days, before the shops act came in yo
u had a job to get closed, they used to come in all hours. Sometimes 'til ten o'clock at night sometimes. Well they used to leave a note and go to the pictures and come back for them just before we closed. Nine - nine - nine o'clock, yes, sometimes later.
 That's before the - Shops Act came in, then when it came we had to close then they had to come early. Closed at nine I think. Yes, used to be open at night - night on a Saturday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you find contact with the customers easy or difficult, could you talk to them quite well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes, no, no, no, they were nice people. Yes. Found them very easy to get on with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 There wasn't another assistant was there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Just ourselves. My uncle wasn't in the shop much, we did it between us. 'Cos he had th
e garden for so many years, then he had to give it up. Yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did all the customers treat you in the same way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Yes. All very nice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you think your aunt and uncle were content with their station in life or do you think they would have liked a higher position?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They seemed - seemed content.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What did you think about your aunt and uncle's way of living?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh they were very particular about everything. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 
And very clean and very, very - prompt with everything.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were you happy there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, very happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did their manners and general behaviour seem different from people you'd met before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, not very much different I don't think. They were very good to get on with, very good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So you stayed there until just before the first world war and then you went.....?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I was with them in the first world war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 When it started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 This same aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. And then the other - they just stayed the year - they only stayed a year after the first world war, then they moved you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 After it started?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So they left about 1915 then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. That's when they moved, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How old would you be then at that time, you were with them about ten years then were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well - I was - I was three and a half years with Alice, with my husband's people, after - after they left you see. Eight and a half and }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 nine}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  - that's twelve years isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So they left during the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. They left a year after the war started.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So that's about 1915 they left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You stayed on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Another three and a half years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who with?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 With - with another aunt and uncle, but it was my husband's people, I married a cousin you see. Yes. Same name - same name
 you see, Claxton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you do exactly the same sort of work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Yes, Same, but I had to work quite so hard. It wasn't so hard with them. They didn't have so many - didn't bother with chickens and things like they did. Fruit and vegetables and - and I used to get a wage with them. About ten shillings a week
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you do the housework as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, I did both.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What hours did you work then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Just for - when there were anything to do. We opened about eight, we closed - we had the prop
er shop hours in them days then. Closed on a Wednesday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you work Saturday and Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Worked Saturday, not Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have a half day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, Wednesday.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Holidays with pay? I got paid every week with them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have any holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No, sometimes I went to Thirsk - home like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 But no proper holidays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they pay you when you went home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They would pay me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And you got ten shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 And they paid me fare when I went - home, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you feel this ten shillings was a fair wage or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well in them days I didn't worry you see, I had to put it away you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you give any of that money to your mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't remember now, I used to put most of it away. Yes, save up, I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you get on with this aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they have any other people to help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 No no-one.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was your }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423226\charrsid9257172 future}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  husband living there as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well he was in - he was working as a tailor in them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was he away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
No, he was at home. At home for so long. And then - and then he - then he left and went to Manchester to learn to - for motor driving, then - then he was only there a
 few years and when he got - when he got - how old would he be then - about eighteen or twenty when he went to Manchester.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So when you were living there he was away was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, I know he was there the first few years then he went - he went to 
Manchester. And got a job there 'cos he went to learn motor driving and he got a job there. He - he didn't like tailoring, wasn't plenty of money you see, it was a small wage. He get a better wage with motor driving. He used to come home every Christmas t
o see us. He lodged with his brother, his brother lived at Manchester you see and he lodged with them. 'Til we got married.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did you get on with this aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh very well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 How did they treat you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Very well indeed. I got better clothes and everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you like the work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
I think they were better off than the other ones I think. I'd get nice clothes. Well I - I - I bought clothes, you see, she gave me a wage so I always paid something for clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You say there were no other servants there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They just treated you as one of the family did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, just treated me like that - like themselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she ever give you any moral guidance, were you allowed out at any time to do what you liked or could you go out when you liked?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I could go if I wanted, I didn't go out very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she mind what you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 If there was anything at the church I used to go to it. That's all, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would your auntie have let you go where you wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 If I'd wanted to, yes. She wouldn't have worried.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was there anything you liked or disliked about living with this aunt and uncle?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, nothing to dislike about either of them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who did the housework there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well I did most of it. Except cleaning time, then they got help in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was the washing sent out or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, she sent all her washing out. Practically all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who made or mended the family clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 The - my aunt mended them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who did the cooking?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 She did most of the cooking. - She learnt me how to cook as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Because she knew you were going to be a daughter-in-law?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, but before - yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Before she knew that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who was responsible for repairs and improvements to the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I think my uncle - I think uncle - both of them I think used to work together with everything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So most of the time you were there it was your aunt and uncle and you was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Your future husband was away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 He was at Manchester working then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Where did you have your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 In - in the living room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was it still a gas cooker?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Yes, a gas cooker. Had ordinary fire in the kitchen.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have breakfast together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Generally, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 About - eight - about eight o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What sort of things would you have for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Generally just marmalade or - bacon if you wanted it, it was there if you wanted it, we didn't always want bacon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was it different on Sunday at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometime a bit different, egg - eggs and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 bacon}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What would you have to drink with your breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Tea generally.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you still have a snack in the middle of the day and your main meal at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, we had - we had our - yes, we had the main meal at night when the shop was open, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you eat the same sort of meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Except Sunday - all had the same. But on the Sunday we had a nicer dinner because there were more time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were the meals with the second aunt and uncle any different from the first aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh no different much, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 Were any of the following made by your second aunt and uncle, did she make her own bread?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she make jam or bottle fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 She made jam sometimes, she bought bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 Did she bottle fruit or vegetables?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 The first aunt did make bread for one while but not for very - not very long. She mostly bought it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your second aunt bottle any fruit or vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 She bottled fruit sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she make any pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't remember, don't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she make wine or beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, don't think so, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they have a garden or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, they hadn't a garden, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they ever buy any tinned or dried vegetables or fruit, did they get those out of the shop or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. We used to sell them I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they keep any livestock?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Now how many times a week was meat eaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well practically every day, some kind of meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Can you remember anything you did with that family on Christmas Day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Sometimes - sometimes we had visitors and sometimes we went to the people round there. Yes. Sometimes - I - sometimes I used to go home for Christmas.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were there any musical instruments in that house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 There was an organ. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6423226\charrsid9257172 American}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  organ that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who played it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 My husband used to play that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 When he wasn't there who played it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 It didn't get played much, only when they came home. It only g
ot played when they came. 'Cos his brother lived at Manchester and he - and they often used to come home together for a - holiday. On holidays.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was there anyone in that family who sang?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever make music together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, not very much.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were there any books in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, there were plenty of books if you wanted to - read.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Any newspapers or magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, used to get a newspaper every day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Any magazines?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't know, don't remember about them. Don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember your aunt or uncle reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes - no, don't remember them reading much, they were different to the other ones.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they ever read aloud to each other?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you remember a funeral in this family before the end of the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Don't remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever go away on holiday or to stay with people with this aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Only - only to relations.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever go away with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Never went away in - when in the shop, they were too busy. Never had a holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did this aunt and uncle think it wrong to work or play on Sunday?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh yes, we never worked on a Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, they went to Wesley - Wesleyan church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they go every Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Mostly. But uncle wasn't well in the end but aunt - auntie used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 When they could they went together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, when they could they went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you still carry on going to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, I still went.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you sit with them when you went to chapel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was grace said at meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, they didn't - they didn't worry about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they ever have family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did this aunt and uncle take an interest in politics at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No - well a little maybe. He was - he was a bit older that uncle you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you know what he was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 remember}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  what they were. Be Liberal I think. I think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your uncle take part in sport?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Too old - no, he was older than the other uncle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Go to the races, play cards or go to a club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
No. He was - he was a - what did he do now this uncle, oh he was a trimmer right up to - right up to - leaving work. It was very hard job wasn't it.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt go out on her own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, she never got out much on her own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she have any interests at all outside the home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't think so. I really I - only like the church she used to go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did she ever work for charities or sit on committees?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, don't think so. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle ever go out together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Sometimes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Where would they go?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They'd go to Hartlepool, the seaside I should think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You say your uncle was a trimmer as well as owning the shop?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 But he gave up when they were in the shop. He gave up - after being there a few years he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid6423226\charrsid9257172 gave}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  up 'cos he - tool old you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Was he ever away from home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't think so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt ever go away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they have friends calling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, had enough friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they come to stay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, well there's some relations come to stay, that was all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What kind of people came?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Some - some relations on her side used to come from Leith. Used to come for a holiday now - only now and again, not very often.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What kind of friends would they have in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh very nice friends.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they usually come for meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, not often. Just ; just to call to see how they were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would you say they were the same class as your aunt and uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What sort of class would you say that was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Very nice people, same as the other aunt and uncle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What sort of class would you call it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What did - what did I say before. Yes. You were working all the time weren't you.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would you say your aunt was the same class as your uncle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle treat some of their friends differently from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle treat any of their friends differently from others?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Treated them alike. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you think your aunt and uncle were content with their station if life, or do you think they would have liked a higher position?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 They seemed - seemed happy enough.
 The uncle you see was a lot older you see than aunt you see because she was his second wife. He - he died while we were there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did the manners and general behaviour of your aunt and uncle seem different from people you'd mixed with before?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No, seemed pretty much the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Have you had any jobs since the first world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Oh I never - I never go out to work. No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would you have preferred another type of occupation than helping in a shop land living in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I don't think so, I was quite happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you belong to a trade union at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, they didn't bother in them days did they.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you feel that employers and workers had the same interests or different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't know, much the same I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Did you feel that there were divisions of interest among workers, some people say that in those days there was a great division between trained craftsmen and other workers? Did you feel that or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes I did. I believe there was among - among some people. Only certain - only; certain ones though.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What sort of difference?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I don't know really. Anyone who had - had a better job was perhaps though a bit more of I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Would you say that full time work changed your general }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 attitude}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No I don't think so. Were always happy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You didn't live at home after you left school did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did starting full time work change your relationship with your mother and step-father at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did it change your relationship with your brother and your sisters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you spend your Sunday any differently now you'd left school, you were living at Hartlepool then but you still went to chapel didn't you?

\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Still went to chapel yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, never thought of it. I think they were all - they were all - as far as I remember they were Liberals.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you take an interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I never bothered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What were your views?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No idea now really. I never used to bother about it you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What about now, are you Liberal now?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Don't know what - now what did I vote last time? Forgotten now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 So you didn't take a particular interest in politics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, I didn't bother with politics really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Do you ever remember voting in a general election before the end of the first world war, before 1919?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Or what party you voted for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I didn't vote 'til after we were married I don't think. We used to vote Liberal then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever feel under any pressure from anyone to vote for a particular party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No, never used - never used to worry.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were you a member of a political party?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever work for one of the parties at an election?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever take part in any political activity other than at election time?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You told me earlier something of how you spent your spare time, did you continue to spend your spare time in the same way or did you d
o different things now you'd left school? How did you spend your spare time when you were living at Hartlepool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I used to go - we used to go to the promenade, I know that. To the seaside.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You liked the sea air did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, because it was like - it was a - tramline in those days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you go on the tram?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
Yes, used to go often to Hartlepool. Just off for a - in the summer we used to go in the evening and used to go on a Sunday sometime. That was lovely there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you go out in the evening at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. Often went - often went out in the evening.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Who would you go with? With this girl next door that you mentioned?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometime - no, sometimes on my own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever go anywhere else in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometimes with my aunt, she used to go sometimes. She was often poorly.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you go anywhere else in the evening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No I don't remember. Only when I went home for weekends, that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you make any new friends, boys or girls, at this time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Except the girl who lived next door?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Next door, that's the only one, and she left after a while.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You just met her because she was next door did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. She lived next door all the time I was in the shop at - with the first
 aunt and uncle you see, and after that she got married you see. It was after me though, she got married after I did, but -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever bring friends home to Hartlepool?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Don't remember.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you have any special friends at this time, any boys or girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 No. Don't remember, only - only people at the church like. Girls at the church. We used to -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever go out with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Sometime we'd go round the prom together.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Where would you go with the girl next door?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well I wouldn't go far with her, just used to see her every day with living there you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle at Hartlepool meet your friends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 We had plenty of friends at church, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You had as well?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes, we both had, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did your aunt and uncle expect to know where you were?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Well I never went out much without them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you ever have to be home by a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 I never - I was never out late.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did you say you were in Hartlepool during the bombardment?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 What do you remember about that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
The bombardment, I was the - I was with the first aunt and uncle. They were just - he was just coming downstairs and he says, the Germans are coming, going to be war, and he didn't know it was true an
d the Germans were there. He just said it as a joke coming downstairs, uncle, coming downstairs for breakfast, eight o'clock. He said, listen the Germans are coming, there's going to be war. And when we looked out there were people dropping in the street,
 dropping - we saw people - dropping down dead in the street. Yes. Terrible. 1914.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Did they bombard straight away then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Yes. We - we - without any }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 warning}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 , yes. He was only doing it - just saying that as a joke. Sit all come true you see. Oh it 
was terrible the first war, that's why they left, they got - got the wind up. They got too worried cos there's that many bombs - that many air raids. Then in the second war as well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 You were then living with your husband in Hartlepool in the second world war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 
When was the second world war was? I know - I know he was just coming downstairs and he was joking and - he used to often joke about - often used to say - there's any noise, the Germans are coming there's going to be war, just in fun, just in a }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 joke}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  and he didn't know it was true. And when I come downstairs all the breakfast table was all littered with glass, all the }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 window}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  was in. Oh our breakfast was ruined, never had any. The lady - the lady across the road shouted across for me and I - I 
just ran across, just a minute or two, and I got me eye cut above and below, with the glass. As a bomb went - as a - not a bomb, as a shell went through the door as I came -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799329 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Were they shelling from ships?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14291105 AC  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172 Then when the war - there was a - yes, f
rom the sea. From Hartlepool West and that's where I was you know and I was across the road. When I come back all me face was covered with blood, was in such a state when they saw me. And we had - we had to queue for the chemist, all me hair was stuck to 
me face. I always remember that, we had - we had to queue for the chemist to get treated because you couldn't go to the doctor while nights you see. This was early morning. Eight o'clock in the morning}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2767346\charrsid9257172 .}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid9701706\charrsid9257172  Never forget that. It was terrible. It was just a joke amongst us you see and it happened to come true.
\par }}